resources.string: Blink! \nJust sit back and work \nand I will remind you to blink in every %s min.
Relax!\n You had enough of work.
We will notify you to blink in every %s min, until you shut it off!
You can not select interval more than 20 min, well its not good for your eyes.
You can not select interval less than 5 min, well its not good to loose concentration now and then.
If you reject this, you wont be able to use this app
